### Cebelca.biz API — playground
### Env vars come from http-client.private.env.json (select "production" in IntelliJ).
### Public API auth = HTTP Basic, api_key as user + literal "x" as pass.
### IntelliJ shorthand: `Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x` (two tokens → user/pass).

@host = https://www.cebelca.biz
@api = {{host}}/API

### =====================================================================
### EXPLORE MODE (_x=1) — discover resources, methods, args
### =====================================================================

### List all resources
POST {{api}}?_x=1
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### List methods of a resource
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent&_x=1
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### List required args of a method
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent&_m=insert-into&_x=1
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### =====================================================================
### PARTNERS (contacts / customers)
### =====================================================================

### All partners
POST {{api}}?_r=partner&_m=select-all
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### One partner by id
POST {{api}}?_r=partner&_m=select-one
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

id=7

### Find-or-create partner (idempotent) — captures id into {{partner_id}}
POST {{api}}?_r=partner&_m=assure
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=My Test Company&street=Downing street 10&postal=E1w201&city=London

> {%
    client.global.set("partner_id", response.body[0][0].id);
%}

### =====================================================================
### ITEMS / SERVICES (pricelist)
### =====================================================================

### All items/services
POST {{api}}?_r=item&_m=select-all
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### Item by code
POST {{api}}?_r=item&_m=select-by-code
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

code=A101

### =====================================================================
### INVOICES (sent) — heads, lines, payments
### =====================================================================

### All invoice heads
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent&_m=select-all
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### Next invoice title/number
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent&_m=select-next-title
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### Invoice line items (bodies)
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent-b&_m=select-all
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### Invoice items/services on bodies (joined)
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent-o&_m=select-all-w-items
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### Invoice payments
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent-p&_m=select-all
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### --- WRITE: empty insert → 403 validation error (shows required fields) ---
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent&_m=insert-into
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### --- WRITE: create invoice head (dates are DD.MM.YYYY) → captures {{invoice_id}} ---
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent&_m=insert-into
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

date_sent=21.07.2026&date_to_pay=31.07.2026&date_served=21.07.2026&id_partner={{partner_id}}

> {%
    client.global.set("invoice_id", response.body[0][0].id);
%}

### --- WRITE: add a line item to that invoice ---
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent-b&_m=insert-into
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

title=Programiranje&qty=10&mu=kos&price=120&vat=22&discount=0&id_invoice_sent={{invoice_id}}

### --- WRITE: record a payment ---
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent-p&_m=insert-into
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

date_of=21.07.2026&amount=120&id_payment_method=1&id_invoice_sent={{invoice_id}}

### --- WRITE: finalize invoice WITHOUT fiscal (non-cash) ---
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent&_m=finalize-invoice-2015
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

id={{invoice_id}}

### --- WRITE: finalize invoice WITH FURS fiscalization ---
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent&_m=finalize-invoice
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

id={{invoice_id}}

### Fiscal info (ZOI/EOR) for an invoice
POST {{api}}?_r=invoice-sent&_m=get-fiscal-info
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

id={{invoice_id}}

### Invoice PDF (separate endpoint, GET)
GET {{host}}/API-pdf?id={{invoice_id}}&format=PDF&res=invoice-sent&lang=si&disposition=inline&preview=0
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x

### =====================================================================
### PROFORMA / ESTIMATES
### =====================================================================

### All proforma heads
POST {{api}}?_r=preinvoice&_m=select-all
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### Proforma line items
POST {{api}}?_r=preinvoice-b&_m=select-all
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### =====================================================================
### STATISTICS
### =====================================================================

### Top customers for a year
POST {{api}}?_r=stat&_m=top-customers
Authorization: Basic {{api_key}} x
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

year=2026&page=-1

### =====================================================================
### UI BACKEND (session cookie) — for resources NOT on the public API
### Run "UI: login" first; IntelliJ persists the RSPSID cookie automatically.
### =====================================================================

### UI: seed session cookie
GET {{host}}/manage/sign-in.html

### UI: login (POST form fields email / password / sign-in)
POST {{host}}/manage/sign-in.html
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email={{user}}&password={{pass}}&sign-in=Vstopite

### UI: company profile (my-company — 404 on public API)
POST {{host}}/manage/DR-srv-pl.html?_r=my-company&_m=select-all
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### UI: invoice with joined line items (same protocol, session auth)
POST {{host}}/manage/DR-srv.html?_r=invoice-sent-o&_m=select-all-w-items
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

###
